sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Nguoi dung
    participant FE as Chat UI
    participant API as Feedback API
    participant DB as Feedback DB
    participant Queue as Improvement Queue
    participant Admin as NLP/RAG Admin
    participant Dataset as Training Dataset

    U->>FE: Bam like/dislike va nhap gop y
    FE->>API: POST /feedback {messageId, rating, comment}
    API->>DB: Luu feedback gan voi cau hoi/cau tra loi
    alt Feedback tieu cuc
        API->>Queue: Tao task review
        Queue-->>Admin: Dua vao hang doi cai thien
        Admin->>Dataset: Sua response, rule, story hoac bo sung tai lieu RAG
    else Feedback tich cuc
        API->>DB: Ghi nhan tin hieu chat luong
    end
    API-->>FE: Da ghi nhan feedback
